sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as "AI Platform"
    participant SSEEndpoint as "GET /mcp/sse"
    participant Transport as "SSEServerTransport"
    participant Sessions as "sessions Map"
    participant MCPServer as "MCP Server"
    participant Messages as "POST /mcp/messages"
    
    Note over Client,Messages: Connection
    Client->>SSEEndpoint: GET /mcp/sse<br/>Accept: text/event-stream
    SSEEndpoint->>Transport: new SSEServerTransport('/mcp/messages', res)
    SSEEndpoint->>MCPServer: buildMcpServer(client)
    SSEEndpoint->>MCPServer: server.connect(transport)
    SSEEndpoint->>Sessions: sessions.set(transport.sessionId, {<br/>transport, server, res, heartbeat, type: 'sse'})
    Transport->>Transport: start() - sends endpoint event
    Transport-->>Client: SSE stream (event: endpoint)
    SSEEndpoint->>SSEEndpoint: setInterval heartbeat (20s)
    
    Note over Client,Messages: JSON-RPC Messages
    Client->>Messages: POST /mcp/messages?sessionId=xyz<br/>JSON-RPC request body
    Messages->>Sessions: sessions.get(sessionId)
    Sessions-->>Messages: {transport, server}
    Messages->>Transport: handlePostMessage(req, res, body)
    Transport->>MCPServer: Process JSON-RPC
    MCPServer-->>Transport: Response
    Transport->>Client: SSE event via stream
    Messages-->>Client: 200 OK (ack)
    
    Note over Client,Messages: Connection Close
    Client->>Client: Close connection
    SSEEndpoint->>SSEEndpoint: res.on('close') event
    SSEEndpoint->>Sessions: clearInterval(heartbeat)<br/>sessions.delete(sessionId)